<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #1a5f2a; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
    .success { color: #1a5f2a; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>2026 Airport Week Golf Tournament</h1>
      <p>Edward A.P. Muna II Memorial</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Great News, <%= @golfer.name %>!</h2>

      <p class="success">ðŸŽ‰ Your spot has been confirmed!</p>

      <p>A spot has opened up and you've been moved from the waitlist to confirmed status for the 2026 Airport Week Golf Tournament.</p>

      <h3>Your Details:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @golfer.name %></li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @golfer.email %></li>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> Confirmed</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Status:</strong> <%= @golfer.payment_status&.capitalize %></li>
      </ul>

      <% if @golfer.payment_status == 'unpaid' %>
        <p><strong>Reminder:</strong> Please complete your payment before the tournament.</p>
      <% end %>

      <p>We look forward to seeing you at the tournament!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Airport Week Golf Tournament</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

